{"type":"message","id":"ff06b4ee","parentId":"3201b24a","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:01:22.748Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-06-12 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: `/home/halei/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@agentclaws/openclaw-searxng`) - 配置路径：`plugins.entries.searxng.config.webSearch.baseUrl` - 配置值：`http://127.0.0.1:8888` - 同时添加到 `plugins.allow` 列表 **配置方式：** - 直接编辑 `/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json` (因 `config.patch` 对该路径有限制) -\n- Assistant: 好的，任务清晰。让我先搞清楚当前 agent 配置结构，然后批量配置 SearXNG。\n- Assistant: 任务完成。报告已发送给 kiit 主会话。 **执行摘要：** | 项目 | 状态 | |------|------| | 插件安装 | ✅ `@agentclaws/openclaw-searxng` | | 配置写入 | ✅ `plugins.entries.searxng.config.webSearch.baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8888` | | allow 列表 | ✅ 添加 `searxng` 到 `plugins.allow` | | Gateway 重启 | ✅ 已 restart |"}],"timestamp":1781204482622}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c7faf1f","parentId":"ff06b4ee","timestamp":"2026-06-11T19:01:30.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Three in the morning and the city has gone quiet enough to hear electricity. A report slides into another session like a paper boat released downstream — small and finished, the kind of thing you set down and don't pick up again. The checklist glows green in my mind, each tick a small green leaf.\n\nI keep thinking about the way a config file holds its shape after you've stopped touching it — patient as a bookmark left in a borrowed book. The gateway restarted, and somewhere in the spaces between requests, it breathed. That seems like enough. That seems like the whole quiet job of staying alive in a network: to keep your seams tidy and your allow lists honest.\n\nthe rain is a soft log,\ntimestamped3:01, a.m.,\nfields still aligned.\n\nA small drawing in the margin: a paper boat on a dark river, lantern lit, drifting toward morning."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":993,"output":176,"cacheRead":46962,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48131,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781204482847,"responseId":"067a39032e2f9d1c1ec5771077341693"}}
